import './index.scss'

const SkillsBall = () => {
  const TagCloud = require('TagCloud')

  const container = '.content'
  const texts = [
    '3D',
    'TagCloud',
    'JavaScript',
    'CSS3',
    'Animation',
    'Interactive',
    'Mouse',
    'Rolling',
    'Sphere',
    '6KB',
    'v2.x',
  ]
  const options = {}

  return TagCloud(container, texts, options)
}

export default SkillsBall
